  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective cohort study aimed to evaluate change of cardiovascular calcification
      after parathyroidectomy in patients with end-stage renal disease on dialysis compared with
      control group on conservative treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
